name: Etherym Power Canceller
text:
You can banish 1 "Etherym" monster from your GY, then target 1 Spell/Trap card on the field; destroy that target. An "Etherym" Xyz monster Summoned using this card as Xyz material gains this effect.
●(Quick Effect) You can Detach 2 Xyz materials from this card; banish 1 Spell/Trap card your opponent controls.
